<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَدَّ الظِّلَّ}</span> ... بَسَطَهُ مِنْ طُلُوعِ الفَجْرِ إِلَى طُلُوعِ الشَّمْسِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَاكِنًا}</span> ... ثَابِتًا مُسْتَقِرًّا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٤٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِبَاسًا}</span> ... سَاتِرًا لَكُمْ بِظَلَامِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٤٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُبَاتًا}</span> ... رَاحَةً لِأَبْدَانِكُمْ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نُشُورًا}</span> ... وَقْتًا لِلِانْتِشَارِ وَالسَّعْيِ فيِ الأَرْضِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بُشْرًا}</span> ... مُبَشِّرَاتٍ بِالرَّحْمَةِ، وَهِيَ المَطَرُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{صَرَّفْنَاهُ}</span> ... أَنْزَلْنَا المَطَرَ عَلَى أَرْضٍ دُونَ أُخْرَى.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَجَاهِدْهُم بِهِ}</span> ... بَلِّغْهُمُ القُرْآنَ بَاذِلًا وُسْعَكَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٥٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جِهَادًا كَبِيرًا}</span> ... لَا يُخِالِطُهُ فُتُورٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَرَجَ}</span> ... خَلَطَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فُرَاتٌ}</span> ... شَدِيدُ العُذُوبَةِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُجَاجٌ}</span> ... شَدِيدُ المُلُوحَةِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَرْزَخًا}</span> ... حَاجِزًا يَمْنَعُ إِفْسَادَ أَحَدِهِمَا لِلآخَرِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَحِجْرًا مَّحْجُورًا}</span> ... سِتْرًا يَمْنَعُ وُصُولَ أَحَدِهِمَا إِلَى الآخَرِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَاءِ}</span> ... مَنِيِّ الرَّجُلِ وَالمَرْأَةِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
